    <briefdescription>
<para>Min-heap priority queue for simulation events, ordered by time with FIFO tiebreaking. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Backed by a <computeroutput>SortedSet&lt;SimEvent&gt;</computeroutput> which exploits <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_sim_event" kindref="compound">SimEvent</ref>&apos;s <computeroutput>IComparable</computeroutput> implementation to maintain heap order without a separate comparator. A monotonically increasing _sequence counter is stamped onto each event at enqueue time to guarantee stable FIFO ordering among events with identical timestamps. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
